    "body": "Let me try to clarify my \"problem\" with the hijacker a bit...\n- He is now much more useful than he was before, you can actually steal a vehicle. :heavy_check_mark: \n- I do agree with @penev92 that it should take some skill to capture a vehicle (but probably just in a way that if you start chasing a vehicle too late it might get away or that the vehicle has a (small) chance to crush you...)\n- However the \"jumping backwards\" behavior @MicroJOo described feels like a bug and the player probably feels it's not his fault for not succeeding.\n"
